1:1 paulov kai silouanov kai timoyeov th ekklhsia yessalonikewn
 en yew patri kai kuriw ihsou cristw: cariv umin kai eirhnh
 apo yeou patrov hmwn kai kuriou ihsou cristou.

1:2 eucaristoumen tw yew pantote peri pantwn umwn mneian
 umwn poioumenoi epi twn proseucwn hmwn,
1:3 adialeiptwv mnhmoneuontev umwn tou ergou thv pistewv
 kai tou kopou thv agaphv kai thv upomonhv thv elpidov tou
 kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou emprosyen tou yeou kai patrov
 hmwn,
1:4 eidotev, adelfoi hgaphmenoi upo yeou, thn ekloghn umwn,
1:5 oti to euaggelion hmwn ouk egenhyh eiv umav en logw
 monon, alla kai en dunamei kai en pneumati agiw kai en
 plhroforia pollh, kaywv oidate oioi egenhyhmen en umin
 di umav:

1:6 kai umeiv mimhtai hmwn egenhyhte kai tou kuriou dexamenoi
 ton logon en yliqei pollh meta carav pneumatov agiou,
1:7 wste genesyai umav tupouv pasin toiv pisteuousin en th
 makedonia kai [en] th acaia.
1:8 af umwn gar exhchtai o logov tou kuriou: ou monon en
 th makedonia kai en th acaia, alla kai en panti topw h
 pistiv umwn h prov ton yeon exelhluyen, wste mh creian
 hmav ecein lalein ti:
1:9 autoi gar peri hmwn apaggellousin opoian eisodon escomen
 prov umav, kai pwv epestreqate prov ton yeon apo twn eidwlwn
 douleuein yew zwnti kai alhyinw,
1:10 kai anamenein ton uion autou ek twn ouranwn, on hgeiren
 ek twn nekrwn, ihsoun ton ruomenon hmav apo thv orghv thv
 ercomenhv.

2:1 autoi gar oidate, adelfoi, thn eisodon hmwn thn prov
 umav oti ou kenh gegonen,
2:2 alla propayontev kai ubrisyentev, kaywv oidate, en filippoiv,
 eparrhsiasameya en tw yew hmwn lalhsai prov umav to euaggelion
 tou yeou en pollw agwni.
2:3 h gar paraklhsiv hmwn ouk ek planhv oude ex akayarsiav,
 oute en dolw,
2:4 alla kaywv dedokimasmeya upo tou yeou pisteuyhnai to
 euaggelion, outwv laloumen, ouc wv anyrwpoiv areskontev,
 alla tw yew tw dokimazonti tav kardiav hmwn.
2:5 oute gar pote en logw kolakeiav egenhyhmen, kaywv oidate,
 oute en profasei pleonexiav, yeov martuv,

2:6 oute zhtountev ex anyrwpwn doxan, oute af umwn oute
 apo allwn, dunamenoi en barei einai wv cristou apostoloi,
2:7 all egenhyhmen hpioi en mesw umwn, wv an trofov yalph ta eauthv tekna:
2:8 outwv omeiromenoi umwn eudokoumen metadounai umin ou
 monon to euaggelion tou yeou, alla kai tav eautwn qucav,
 dioti agaphtoi hmin gegenhsye.
2:9 mnhmoneuete gar, adelfoi, ton kopon hmwn kai ton mocyon:
 nuktov gar kai hmerav ergazomenoi prov to mh epibarhsai
 tina umwn ekhruxamen eiv umav to euaggelion tou yeou.
2:10 umeiv marturev kai o yeov wv osiwv kai dikaiwv kai
 amemptwv umin toiv pisteuousin egenhyhmen,
2:11 kayaper oidate wv ena ekaston umwn wv pathr tekna eautou
parakalountev umav kai paramuyoumenoi
2:12 kai marturomenoi eiv to peripathsai umav axiwv tou yeou tou
 kalountov umav eiv thn eautou basileian kai doxan.
2:13 dia touto kai hmeiv eucaristoumen tw yew adialeiptwv,
 oti paralabontev logon akohv par hmwn tou yeou edexasye
 ou logon anyrwpwn, alla kaywv estin alhywv, logon yeou,
 ov kai energeitai en umin toiv pisteuousin.
2:14 umeiv gar mimhtai egenhyhte, adelfoi, twn ekklhsiwn
 tou yeou twn ouswn en th ioudaia en cristw ihsou, oti ta
 auta epayete kai umeiv upo twn idiwn sumfuletwn kaywv kai
 autoi upo twn ioudaiwn,
2:15 twn kai ton kurion apokteinantwn ihsoun kai touv idiouv
 profhtav, kai hmav ekdiwxantwn, kai yew mh areskontwn,
 kai pasin anyrwpoiv enantiwn,
2:16 kwluontwn hmav toiv eynesin lalhsai ina swywsin, eiv
 to anaplhrwsai autwn tav amartiav pantote. efyasen de ep
 autouv h orgh eiv telov.

2:17 hmeiv de, adelfoi, aporfanisyentev af umwn prov kairon
 wrav, proswpw ou kardia, perissoterwv espoudasamen to proswpon
 umwn idein en pollh epiyumia.
2:18 dio hyelhsamen elyein prov umav, egw men paulov kai
 apax kai div, kai enekoqen hmav o satanav.
2:19 tiv gar hmwn elpiv h cara h stefanov kauchsewv h ouci
 kai umeiv emprosyen tou kuriou hmwn ihsou [cristou] en th
 autou parousia;
2:20 umeiv gar este h doxa hmwn kai cara.

3:1 dio mhketi stegontev eudokhsamen kataleifyhnai en ayhnaiv
 monoi,
3:2 kai epemqamen timoyeon, ton adelfon hmwn kai diakonon
 tou yeou kai sunergon hmwn en tw euaggeliw tou cristou,
 eiv to sthrixai umav kai parakalesai umav peri thv pistewv
 umwn,
3:3 to mhdena sainesyai en taiv yliqesin tautaiv. autoi gar
 oidate oti eiv touto keimeya:
3:4 kai gar ote prov umav hmen, proelegomen umin oti mellomen
 ylibesyai, kaywv kai egeneto kai oidate.
3:5 dia touto kagw mhketi stegwn epemqa eiv to gnwnai thn
 pistin umwn, mh pwv epeirasen umav o peirazwn kai eiv kenon
 genhtai o kopov hmwn.
3:6 arti de elyontov timoyeou prov hmav af umwn kai euaggelisamenou
 hmin thn pistin kai thn agaphn umwn, kai oti ecete mneian
 hmwn agayhn, pantote epipoyountev hmav idein kayaper kai
 hmeiv umav,
3:7 dia touto pareklhyhmen, adelfoi, ef umin epi pash th
 yliqei kai anagkh hmwn dia thv umwn pistewv:
3:8 oti nun zwmen, ean umeiv sthkhte en kuriw.
3:9 tina gar eucaristian dunameya tw yew antapodounai peri
 umwn epi pash th cara h cairomen di umav emprosyen tou
 yeou hmwn,
3:10 nuktov kai hmerav uperekperissou deomenoi eiv to idein
 umwn to proswpon kai katartisai ta usterhmata thv pistewv
 umwn;
3:11 autov de o yeov kai pathr hmwn kai o kuriov hmwn ihsouv
 cristov kateuyunai thn odon hmwn prov umav:
3:12 umav de o kuriov pleonasai kai perisseusai th agaph
 eiv allhlouv kai eiv pantav, kayaper kai hmeiv eiv umav,
3:13 eiv to sthrixai umwn tav kardiav amemptouv en agiwsunh
 emprosyen tou yeou kai patrov hmwn en th parousia tou kuriou
 hmwn ihsou cristou meta pantwn twn agiwn autou.

4:1 to loipon oun, adelfoi, erwtwmen umav kai parakaloumen
 en kuriw ihsou, kaywv parelabete par hmwn to pwv dei umav
 peripatein kai areskein yew, ina perisseuhte mallon:
4:2 oidate gar tinav paraggeliav edwkamen umin dia tou kuriou
 ihsou.
4:3 touto gar estin yelhma tou yeou, o agiasmov umwn, apecesyai
 umav apo thv porneiav,
4:4 eidenai ekaston umwn to eautou skeuov ktasyai en agiasmw
 kai timh,
4:5 mh en payei epiyumiav kayaper kai ta eynh ta mh eidota
 ton yeon,
4:6 to mh uperbainein kai pleonektein en tw pragmati ton
 adelfon autou, dioti ekdikov o kuriov peri pantwn toutwn,
 kaywv kai proeipomen umin kai diemarturameya.
4:7 ou gar ekalesen hmav o yeov epi akayarsia, all en agiasmw.
4:8 toigaroun o ayetwn ouk anyrwpon ayetei, alla ton yeon
 ton [kai] donta to pneuma autou to agion eiv umav.
4:9 peri de thv filadelfiav ou creian ecete grafein umin:
 autoi gar umeiv yeodidaktoi este eiv to agapan allhlouv:
4:10 kai gar poieite auto eiv pantav touv adelfouv touv
 en olh th makedonia. parakaloumen de umav, adelfoi, perisseuein
 mallon
4:11 kai filotimeisyai hsucazein kai prassein ta idia kai
 ergazesyai taiv idiaiv cersin umwn, kaywv umin parhggeilamen,
4:12 ina peripathte euschmonwv prov touv exw kai mhdenov
 creian echte.

4:13 ou yelomen de umav agnoein, adelfoi, peri twn kekoimhmenwn,
 ina mh luphsye kaywv kai oi loipoi oi mh econtev elpida.
4:14 ei gar pisteuomen oti ihsouv apeyanen kai anesth, outwv
 kai o yeov touv koimhyentav dia tou ihsou axei sun autw.
4:15 touto gar umin legomen en logw kuriou, oti hmeiv oi
 zwntev oi perileipomenoi eiv thn parousian tou kuriou
 ou mh fyaswmen touv koimhyentav:
4:16 oti autov o kuriov en keleusmati, en fwnh arcaggelou
 kai en salpiggi yeou katabhsetai ap ouranou, kai oi nekroi
 en cristw anasthsontai prwton,
4:17 epeita hmeiv oi zwntev oi perileipomenoi ama sun autoiv
 arpaghsomeya en nefelaiv eiv apanthsin tou kuriou eiv aera,
 kai outwv pantote sun kuriw esomeya.
4:18 wste parakaleite allhlouv en toiv logoiv toutoiv.

5:1 peri de twn cronwn kai twn kairwn, adelfoi, ou creian
 ecete umin grafesyai:
5:2 autoi gar akribwv oidate oti h hmera kuriou wv klepthv
 en nukti outwv ercetai.
5:3 otan gar legwsin, eirhnh kai asfaleia, tote aifnidiov
 autoiv efistatai oleyrov, wsper h wdin th en gastri ecoush,
 kai ou mh ekfugwsin.
5:4 umeiv de, adelfoi, ouk este en skotei, ina h hmera umav
 wv klepthv katalabh:
5:5 pantev umeiv uioi fwtov este kai uioi hmerav. ouk esmen nuktov oude
 skotouv.
5:6 ara oun mh kayeudwmen wv kai oi loipoi, alla grhgorwmen kai
 nhfwmen.
5:7 oi gar kayeudontev nuktov kayeudousin, kai oi meyuskomenoi
 nuktov meyuousin:
5:8 umeiv de hmerav ontev nhfwmen, endusamenoi ywraka pistewv
 kai agaphv kai perikefalaian elpida swthriav:
5:9 oti ouk eyeto hmav o yeov eiv orghn, all eiv peripoihsin
 swthriav dia tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou,
5:10 tou apoyanontov uper hmwn, ina eite grhgorwmen eite
 kayeudwmen ama sun autw zhswmen.
5:11 dio parakaleite allhlouv kai oikodomeite eiv ton ena,
 kaywv kai poieite.

5:12 erwtwmen de umav, adelfoi, eidenai touv kopiwntav en
 umin kai proistamenouv umwn en kuriw kai nouyetountav umav,
5:13 kai hgeisyai autouv uperekperissou en agaph dia to
 ergon autwn. eirhneuete en eautoiv.
5:14 parakaloumen de umav, adelfoi, nouyeteite touv ataktouv,
 paramuyeisye touv oligoqucouv, antecesye twn asyenwn, makroyumeite
 prov pantav.
5:15 orate mh tiv kakon anti kakou tini apodw, alla pantote
 to agayon diwkete kai eiv allhlouv kai eiv pantav.
5:16 pantote cairete,
5:17 adialeiptwv proseucesye,
5:18 en panti eucaristeite: touto gar yelhma yeou en cristw
 ihsou eiv umav.
5:19 to pneuma mh sbennute,
5:20 profhteiav mh exouyeneite.
5:21 panta [de] dokimazete, to kalon katecete:
5:22 apo pantov eidouv ponhrou apecesye.
5:23 autov de o yeov thv eirhnhv agiasai umav oloteleiv,
 kai oloklhron umwn to pneuma kai h quch kai to swma amemptwv
 en th parousia tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou thrhyeih.
5:24 pistov o kalwn umav, ov kai poihsei.

5:25 adelfoi, proseucesye peri hmwn.
5:26 aspasasye touv adelfouv pantav en filhmati agiw.
5:27 orkizw umav ton kurion anagnwsyhnai thn epistolhn pasin
 toiv agioiv adelfoiv.
5:28 h cariv tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou mey umwn: amhn.
